### ============================================
### AI ENDPOINTS (Rate Limited: 10 req/min)
### ============================================

### Rewrite bullet point
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/rewrite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Worked on various projects"
}

### Improve wording
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/improve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "I did some work on a project"
}

### Generate professional summary
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/generate-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "experience": "Software Engineer with 5 years of experience developing web applications using React, Node.js, and TypeScript.",
  "skills": ["JavaScript", "TypeScript", "React", "Node.js", "PostgreSQL"]
}

### Suggest skills
POST {{baseUrl}}/ai/suggest-skills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "experience": "Worked as a software engineer for 5 years developing web applications using React and Node.js. Led a team of 3 developers and implemented CI/CD pipelines."
}

